modName: Dark Brotherhood Armour for CHSBHC BBP mod
summary: Dark Brotherhood Armour for CHSBHC mod
descriptionHtml:
This is the Dark Brotherhood Armour for the CHSBHC shape.
CHSBHC Shape mod can be found here: http://www.skyrimnexus.com/downloads/file.php?id=4888

This mod simply mods the shape of the armour to follow the overall shape of the CHSBHC and BBP mod

Release 1.1 now includes my BBP (Breast and Butt Physics)

--Features
-Curvier body in the Dark Brotherhood armor
-Slimmer waist
-Works with weight slider in the game

--Installation
Simply extract this to your Skyrim\'s data folder

(will look something like this: \"C:\\Program Files (x86)\\The Elder Scrolls V Skyrim\\Data\\meshes\\armor\\dbarmor\")

Enjoy!

-Cherry Hotaling
